                  , on the <rs id="t17830723-5-cd19" type="crimeDate">30th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830723-5-off18 t17830723-5-cd19"></join> last, in a certain dwelling house of our Lord the King, called <placeName id="t17830723-5-crimeloc20">St. James's Palace</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t17830723-5-crimeloc20" type="placeName" value="St. James's Palace"></interp>
