                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830723-5-off18 t17830723-5-crimeloc20"></join>, and putting him in fear and danger of his life, and taking from his person and against his will, two pieces of gold coin of this realm, called guineas, value 2 l. 2 s. the monies of the said 
